Transmutation
Levels: Sor/Wiz 4
Components: V,S
Range: 10 ft
Targets: All creatures in a 10-ft radius sphere around you at the time of casting
Duration: 1 hour/level
Saving Throw: None
Spell Resistance: Yes (harmless)

As Ultravision, except that all creatures in the area at the time of casting receive the spell's benefits.